cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

The paper proposes a new method for compressing deep neural network models for regression problems using knowledge distillation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses two open datasets, MPIIGaze and Multi-PIE, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a new loss function and a multi-task network, which are related to neural networks (cs.NE) and statistical learning (cs.SD).
